        "text_tQNWNg": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>See the three Oily Sensitive moisturisers: <a href=\"/products/flow-oily-sensitive-a-light-face-moisturiser-for-oily-sensitive-skin\" title=\"Flow — Oily Sensitive, a light face moisturiser for oily, sensitive skin\">Flow</a>, <a href=\"/products/core-oily-sensitive-a-light-body-moisturiser-for-oily-sensitive-skin\" title=\"Core — Oily Sensitive, a light body moisturiser for oily, sensitive skin\">Core</a> and <a href=\"/products/deep-oily-sensitive-a-richer-moisturiser-for-oily-sensitive-skin-for-hands-elbows-and-feet\" title=\"Deep — Oily Sensitive, a richer moisturiser for oily, sensitive skin, for hands, elbows and feet\">Deep</a><br/></li><li>Not sure this is you? <a href=\"/pages/find-your-skin-type\" title=\"Find Your Skin Type\">Find your skin type</a><br/></li><li>The other skin types: <a href=\"/collections/dry-sensitive-skin-type\" title=\"Dry Sensitive Skin Type\">Dry Sensitive</a>, <a href=\"/collections/dry-skin-type\" title=\"Dry Skin Type\">Dry</a>, <a href=\"/collections/balanced-skin-type\" title=\"Balanced Skin Type\">Balanced</a>, <a href=\"/collections/oily\" title=\"Oily Skin Type\">Oily</a><br/></li><li><a href=\"/blogs/ingredients\" title=\"Ingredients\">How we choose our ingredients</a>, and the science behind them</li></ul>",
